Now I understand the situation clearly:                                     
                                                                              
  • OBA_VT0002092 (eye morphology trait) is already imported                  
  • OBA_VT0001321 (pupil size trait) needs to be imported                     
  • In OBA: pupil size trait → eye size trait (OBA_VT0002697, not in EFO) →   
  eye morphology trait (OBA_VT0002092)                                        
  • Since eye size trait is not in EFO, we need to link pupil size trait      
  directly to eye morphology trait via subclasses.csv                         
                                                                              
